settings {
  encodeUrl: true
}

docs {
  **Purpose:** Creates a new user-role assignment in the organization structure.

  **Auth:** Session cookie (`readi_auth_token`). Requires admin permission.

  **Used in:**
  - Organization role assignment forms
}